    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >“BAKUDO” ── 超越想像的究极球类运动</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验 《BAKUDO》别具特色的战斗体验，享受爽快且充满紧张刺激的全新“球技战斗”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进以信念为力量的战场──没有规则，没有限制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选手们赌上所有，无所不用其极，只为成为最强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在“BAKUDO”的赛场上，只有彼此炙热燃烧的信念与斗志──</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/eefb478ec9cb59aa69f4cb318f9eb907.poster.avif?t=1752110790\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/eefb478ec9cb59aa69f4cb318f9eb907.webm?t=1752110790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/eefb478ec9cb59aa69f4cb318f9eb907.mp4?t=1752110790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事的主舞台</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一所专为“BAKUDO”竞技而创立的顶尖学园，学生们为了站上颠峰彼此较劲，因为在这里——实力便是一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将跟随主角“悠莉亚”的脚步，以寻找失踪的父亲为目的来到这所学园就读，并在过程中与各式各样的人物建立起深厚的羁绊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而学园的背后并不那麽单纯，在前方等待着主角的将会是──。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/6584f01511997144710f4c013f09c6d4.poster.avif?t=1752110790\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/6584f01511997144710f4c013f09c6d4.webm?t=1752110790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/6584f01511997144710f4c013f09c6d4.mp4?t=1752110790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>球光交错的攻防战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与眼前强大的Boss展开令人屏息的即时战斗，融合投掷球的攻防对决。打造出节奏明快、风格独特的战斗系统。观察对手，掌握对方的招式与破绽，见招拆招才是致胜关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片燃烧信念的赛场上──</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你，准备好了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/d4ca9f8ae63c09aadb8f5bb3a012c2c5.poster.avif?t=1752110790\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/d4ca9f8ae63c09aadb8f5bb3a012c2c5.webm?t=1752110790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/d4ca9f8ae63c09aadb8f5bb3a012c2c5.mp4?t=1752110790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>位于学园顶峰的八人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角将面对的是称霸学园的人物，独具一格的战斗风格是他们的强大武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/9ee3aefbf0c71359822a80bb1b1f4149.poster.avif?t=1752110790\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/9ee3aefbf0c71359822a80bb1b1f4149.webm?t=1752110790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275860/extras/9ee3aefbf0c71359822a80bb1b1f4149.mp4?t=1752110790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
